

d.scale - 

d.scale displays a bar scale and north arrow relevant to the user's
current @glossary("geographic region",16.glossary/georeg.def) setting in the upper left corner of the
active display @glossary("frame",16.glossary/graphframe.def) on the graphics monitor.  Only those portions of
the active display frame that directly underlie the legend will be
obscured by the legend.

